msgstr "主题集成短代码"

msgid "If your theme has a custom login page, use the following shortcodes to embed Swift Login features into your theme template:"
msgstr "如果您的主题有自定义登录页面，可使用以下短代码将 Swift Login 的功能嵌入到主题模板中："

msgid "Passkey Login Button"
msgstr "Passkey 登录按钮"

