msgstr "在 GitHub 上查看"

msgid "This feature integrates with <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zhiwo Cloud Social Login</a>. Please register on that platform, create an application, and enter the App ID and App Key below."
msgstr "本功能对接 <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">知我云聚合登录</a>，请前往该平台注册并创建应用，获取 App ID 和 App Key 后填入下方。"

